  <brief_title>Comparison of High-Dose Methotrexate (HDM) Plus Doxorubicin to HDM Plus Etoposide-Ifosfamide in Osteosarcoma Children</brief_title>
  <official_title>SFOP-OS94: Multicentric Randomised Phase III Trial Comparing Efficacy of Preoperative High-Dose Methotrexate Plus Doxorubicin to Efficacy of High-Dose Methotrexate Plus Etoposide and Ifosfamide, in Children and Adolescents Osteosarcoma</official_title>
  <sponsors>
