  <source>Gustave Roussy, Cancer Campus, Grand Paris</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare two preoperative chemotherapy regimens based on
      high-dose methotrexate courses given alternately either with doxorubicin or with
      etoposide-ifosfamide.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
